ote Sent - Reminder 4","group_name":"QUOTE","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1121.0\">\r\n<p>Hello <first_name>!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tI hope everything is going well for you. I wanted to follow up on the quote we sent you 14 days ago regarding DJ and entertainment services for your <event_type>. We are still as eager as ever to serve you and make your <event_type> truly unforgettable.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tAt Xpress Entertainment, we understand the importance of finding the perfect DJ and entertainment for your special day. Our team of talented professionals is dedicated to creating an atmosphere that will have your guests talking about your event for years to come.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tWe wanted to reiterate our commitment to meeting your specific needs and exceeding your expectations. If you have any questions, require further information, or would like to discuss any modifications to the quote, please don&#39;t hesitate to reach out. We are here to ensure that every de","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":14,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["a68a9f16-ae52-4442-941a-cc7b9ceed711"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"salesperson","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":["Imported timing anchor “Custom Event Date 2” has no XOS equivalent — pick a send trigger before enabling."]},{"legacy_djep_id":217359,"name":"Event Booking Notification","display_name":"Event Booking Notification","group_name":"EMPLOYEE REMINDER","subject":"","body_html":"Hello, This is notification that an event has been assigned to you! \r\n\r\nThe client has not signed yet, however please check you email for details.\r\n\r\n - Xpress Entertainment","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_