 Time:&nbsp;</strong><setup_time><br />\r\n\t<strong>Start Time: </strong><start_time><br />\r\n\t<strong>End Time:</strong> <end_time><br />\r\n\t<strong>Booking Notes: </strong><comments><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217362,"name":"RE: Looking for a Wedding DJ","display_name":"Wedding Active Lead 7","group_name":"LEADS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1121.0\">\r\n<span style=\"font-family:calibri,verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\"><first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tI just wanted to follow up and make sure you&#39;ve gotten my previous emails.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tDo you have time for a consultation?&nbsp; \r\n\t<a href=\"https://calendly.com/xpressdjs/consultation\">BOOK NOW</a><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tThank you,&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<company_email_signature></span></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":29,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"initial_contact_date","sched_status_ids":["60be24e8-cf5a-46fc-95b7-15090fd1b2fc"],"sched_event_type_ids":["d934d08d-4338-409c-aeda-ec005d10cfad"],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217363,"name":"RE: Looking for a Wedding DJ","display_name":"Wedding Active Lead 8","group_name":"LEADS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1121.0\">\r\n<span style=\"font-family:calibri,verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\"><first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tI just wanted to follow up and make sure you&#39;ve gotten my previous emails.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tDo you have time for a consultation?&nbsp; \r\n\t<a href=\"https://calendly.com/xpressdjs/consultation\">BOOK NOW</a><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tThank you,&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<company_email_signature></span></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":30,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"initial_contact_date","sched_status_ids":["60be24e8-cf5a-46fc-95b7-15090fd1b2fc"],"sched_event_type_ids":["d934d08d-4338-409c-aeda-ec005d10cfad"],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217364,"name":"Hey, . Sorry we missed eachother.","display_name":"Reply - Missed Meeting","group_name":"LEADS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1121.0\">Hey, <first_name>,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJust checking in to see if you had any time available and would like to reschedule our meeting?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<company_email_signature></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217365,"name":"Friendly Reminder: Last Chance to finalize Your Booking with Xpress Entertainment","display_name":"3 Last Day - Retainer Fee","group_name":"PENDING","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1137.0\">Dear <first_name>,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI hope this email finds you well and excited for the upcoming event! We just wanted to send you a quick reminder that today marks the final day for the payment of the&nbsp;<retainer_fee> retainer fee to secure your booking with Xpress Entertainment.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe understand that life gets busy, and deadlines can sometimes slip through the cracks. We truly value the opportunity to be a part of your special celebration and want to ensure everything goes smoothly for you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you have any questions or concerns about the payment process, please don&#39;t hesitate to reach out to us. We&#39;re here to help!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"<client_logon_link>?username=<username>&amp;password=<password>\">Click Here to make a payment</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<company_email_signature>&nbsp;</body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":14,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["146ef586-5622-4302-8212-e074799115f4","c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client","master_admin","salesperson"],"review_reasons":["Imported timing anchor “Custom Event Date 3” has no XOS equivalent — pick a send trigger before enabling."]},{"legacy_djep_id":217366,"name":"days!","display_name":"We're Alive 1 (250 Days)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1217.0\">Hey&nbsp;<first_name>,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe just want to reach out, theres <event_date_countdown> days until the big day!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere isn&#39;t much we need from you until we approach the date, but we will shoot you reminders for planning information and we will go over everything as the date approaches.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe will reach out to set up meetings&nbsp;so you don&#39;t even have to think about it, looking forward to it!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<company_email_signature></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":250,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217367,"name":"days!","display_name":"We're Alive 2 (200 Days)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\">\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch><o:AllowPNG/></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml><![endif]--><!--[if !mso]><!-->\r\n\t<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><!--<![endif]-->\r\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">* {\r\n\t\t\tbox-sizing: border-box;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tbody {\r\n\t\t\tmargin: 0;\r\n\t\t\tpadding: 0;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\ta[x-apple-data-detectors] {\r\n\t\t\tcolor: inherit !important;\r\n\t\t\ttext-decoration: inherit !important;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t#MessageViewBody a {\r\n\t\t\tcolor: inherit;\r\n\t\t\ttext-decoration: none;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tp {\r\n\t\t\tline-height: inherit\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t.desktop_hide,\r\n\t\t.desktop_hide table {\r\n\t\t\tmso-hi","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":200,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review