 just want to reach out, theres <event_date_countdown> days until the big day!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere isn&#39;t much we need from you until we approach the date, but we will shoot you reminders for planning information and we will go over everything as the date approaches.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe will reach out to set up meetings&nbsp;so you don&#39;t even have to think about it, looking forward to it!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<company_email_signature></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":150,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217370,"name":"days! - the excitement is staring to build up!","display_name":"We're Alive 5 (Retired)","group_name":"RETIRED TEMPLATES","subject":"","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\">\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch><o:AllowPNG/></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml><![endif]-->\r\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">* {\r\n\t\t\tbox-sizing: border-box;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tbody {\r\n\t\t\tmargin: 0;\r\n\t\t\tpadding: 0;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\ta[x-apple-data-detectors] {\r\n\t\t\tcolor: inherit !important;\r\n\t\t\ttext-decoration: inherit !important;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t#MessageViewBody a {\r\n\t\t\tcolor: inherit;\r\n\t\t\ttext-decoration: none;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tp {\r\n\t\t\tline-height: inherit\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t.desktop_hide,\r\n\t\t.desktop_hide table {\r\n\t\t\tmso-hide: all;\r\n\t\t\tdisplay: none;\r\n\t\t\tmax-height: 0px;\r\n\t\t\toverflow: hidden;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t.image_block img+div {\r\n\t\t\tdisplay: none;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t@media (max-width:620px) {\r\n\t\t\t.social_block.d","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217371,"name":"This is Xpress Entertainment - Nice to meet you!","display_name":"Wedding Show Lead - 1","group_name":"LEADS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1125.0\">\r\n<p>Hey&nbsp;<first_name>,&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tHere is our contact info,&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tPlease let me know if you have any questions!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tWarm regards,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<company_email_signature></p></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":1,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["22e61d89-1869-4ed3-b759-dddd2d4236f0"],"sched_event_type_ids":["d934d08d-4338-409c-aeda-ec005d10cfad"],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":["Imported timing anchor “Custom Event Date 3” has no XOS equivalent — pick a send trigger before enabling."]},{"legacy_djep_id":217372,"name":"Follow-Up: Your Upcoming Wedding Celebration","display_name":"Wedding Show Lead - 2","group_name":"LEADS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1196.0\">\r\n<p>Hey&nbsp;<first_name>,&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tI hope this message finds you well. It was such a pleasure meeting you at the wedding showcase this past weekend. The energy and excitement surrounding your upcoming wedding were truly infectious!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tWe are genuinely thrilled to be a part of your special day. To ensure we tailor our services perfectly to your vision, we would love to learn more about your dreams and aspirations for this momentous occasion. Please feel free to share any questions or thoughts you may have at this early stage. Your insights are invaluable to us.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tHere is the package that we are offering to couples we have met at the event this past weekend<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>THE XPERIANCE PACKAGE</strong></span><br />\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">Regular Price; $1,750</span> \r\n\t<span style=\"","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":2,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["22e61d89-1869-4ed3-b759-dddd2d4236f0"],"sched_event_type_ids":["d934d08d-4338-409c-aeda-ec005d10cfad"],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":["Imported timing anchor “Custom Event Date 3” has no XOS equivalent — pick a send trigger before enabling."]},{"legacy_djep_id":217373,"name":"Your Entertainment has been Booked!","display_name":"BOOKED EV","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\">\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch><o:AllowPNG/></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml><![endif]-->\r\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">* {\r\n\t\t\tbox-sizing: border-box;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tbody {\r\n\t\t\tmargin: 0;\r\n\t\t\tpadding: 0;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\ta[x-ap