y - Payment(COPY)","group_name":"LEADS","subject":"","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\">\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch><o:AllowPNG/></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml><![endif]-->\r\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">* {\r\n\t\t\tbox-sizing: border-box;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tbody {\r\n\t\t\tmargin: 0;\r\n\t\t\tpadding: 0;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\ta[x-apple-data-detectors] {\r\n\t\t\tcolor: inherit !important;\r\n\t\t\ttext-decoration: inherit !important;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t#MessageViewBody a {\r\n\t\t\tcolor: inherit;\r\n\t\t\ttext-decoration: none;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tp {\r\n\t\t\tline-height: inherit\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t.desktop_hide,\r\n\t\t.desktop_hide table {\r\n\t\t\tmso-hide: all;\r\n\t\t\tdisplay: none;\r\n\t\t\tmax-height: 0px;\r\n\t\t\toverflow: hidden;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t.image_block img+div {\r\n\t\t\tdisplay: none;\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t@media (max-width:660px) {\r\n\t\t\t.mobile_hide {\r","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217379,"name":"Hello , It's time to get Married!(COPY)","display_name":"Wedding Active Lead 1(COPY)","group_name":"LEADS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1136.0\">\r\n<span style=\"font-family:calibri,verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\">Hello <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tWe&#39;d like to take the opportunity to extend our warmest congratulations! We understand that you must be getting a lot of messages and calls from various vendors. So we&#39;ll keep this brief. We&#39;ve seen that you are planning your wedding and want to get some ideas on finding the right entertainment. We feel confident that one of our DJs might be the ideal choice for you.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>Would you have time for a short call where we can discuss the specifics of your event?</strong> More details can lead to a better understanding of what music, DJs, and packages you may require.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tIf you&#39;re interested in checking out our rates, you can \r\n\t<a href=\"https://www.xpressdjs.com/pricing\">CLICK HERE</a> and view our usual packages. If you have any ","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["60be24e8-cf5a-46fc-95b7-15090fd1b2fc"],"sched_event_type_ids":["d934d08d-4338-409c-aeda-ec005d10cfad"],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":["Imported timing anchor “Custom Event Date 3” has no XOS equivalent — pick a send trigger before enabling."]},{"legacy_djep_id":217381,"name":"We're Alive (30 Days)","display_name":"We're Alive (30 Days)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"Xpress Entertainment: \r\n\r\nIt's the final countdown! We are 30 days away from the big day - We sent you an email, please check it out when you have a moment. \r\n\r\nThank you!","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":30,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217382,"name":"We're Alive (10 Days)","display_name":"We're Alive (10 Days)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"Xpress Entertainment: \r\n\r\n10 days away! Have you updated the Vibo App? Communication is key!\r\n\r\nThank you","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":10,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217383,"name":"Invite to Follow us!","display_name":"Invite to Follow us!","group_name":"1 COMMUNITY BUILDING","subject":"","body_html":"Hey <first_name>!\r\n\r\nFollow us on Instagram @xpressdjs! You'll get a chance to win prizes, pick up tips & tricks, check out other weddings we've done, and snag some cool ideas for your big day!\r\n\r\nCheers,\r\nHelen\r\nXpress Entertainment","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":4,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"booked_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":["d934d08d-4338-409c-aeda-ec005d10cfad"],"schedule_from":"company","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217384,"name":"Important: Let’s Make Sure Your DJ is Ready to Rock Your Wedding!","display_name":"Incomplete Vibo","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1270.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1270.0\">Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo help us ensure that your DJ has everything they need to bring your vision to life, we need your help!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease make sure to start or continue filling out your Vibo DJ app. This is where you&rsquo;ll enter your must-play songs, timeline details, and overall vibe. The sooner we get this info, the better we can prepare to make your day perfect!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you haven&rsquo;t downloaded the app yet, here&rsquo;s how:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&#128241; Download for iPhone ( \r\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vibo-2-0/id1523045467\">App Store</a>)<br />\r\n&#128241; Download for Android ( \r\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vibodj&amp;hl=en_US\">Google Play</a>)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOnce downloaded, you can access your event directly here:&#128073; [ \r\n<a href=\"<cu","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217385,"name":"Incomplete Vibo","display_name":"Incomplete Vibo","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"Hi <first_name>, how’s it going with the Vibo DJ app? Any questions or need any help? Here’s the link if you need it: <custom_field7>. Let us know how we can assist you! You can also schedule a meeting if you'd like to go over anything.\r\n\r\nBest,\r\nLaura\r\nXpress Entertainment","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"company","sched_send_to":[],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217386,"name":"Heads up, Payment 2 is due in a week","display_name":"Payment 2 - Reminder 1","group_name":"REMINDERS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1168.0\">Hey <first_name>, just a friendly reminder that your second payment of <second_payment_amount>&nbsp;is due by <second_payment_date>.&nbsp;This is also crunch time to decide if you would like us to add any anything to your package.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"<client_logon_link>?username=<username>&amp;password=<password>\">Click Here to make a payment</a><br />\r\n\tA processing fee will be applied for online payments, to avoid this, we also accept Zelle<br />\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#FFD700;\">If opting to Zelle, attach a note with event date and name on the contract, also inform&nbsp;us immediately</span><br />\r\n\t<strong>Zelle Email: office@xpressdjs.com</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tThank you!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<company_email_signature></p></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":14,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":["Imported timing anchor “Scheduled Payment #2” has no XOS equivalent — pick a send trigger before enabling."]},{"legacy_djep_id":217388,"name":"Booked @ Villa Hello SMS","display_name":"Booked @ Villa Hello SMS","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"Hi <first_name>!\r\n\r\nThis is Laura from Xpress Entertainment. I’m excited to let you know that we’ve officially booked your DJ/entertainment through our partnership with Villa Toscana Miami!\r\n\r\nI've sent you an email, including instructions to download our app. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out!\r\n\r\nBest,\r\nLaura\r\nXpress Entertainment","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"company","sched_send_to":[],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217390,"name":"Our Client is interested in your services!","display_name":"Preferred Vendor Notification","group_name":"VENDORS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1198.0\">\r\n<p>Hello Preferred Vendor,&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tOne of our clients is looking for services in your field and we have recommend you! We have given the client your contact information and wanted to give your their&nbsp;contact information. We&#39;d recommend reaching out as soon as possible, make sure to let them know <salesperson_first_name> from Xpress Entertainment sent you.&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>Event Name:&nbsp;</strong><event_name><br />\r\n\t<strong>Event Date:</strong>&nbsp;<event_date_long><br />\r\n\t<strong>Event Venue:&nbsp;</strong><event_location><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>Client Name:&nbsp;</strong><name><br />\r\n\t<strong>Client Phone Number:</strong>&nbsp;<cell_phone><br />\r\n\t<strong>Client Email:</strong>&nbsp;<email><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tPlease let me know should you have any questions!&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<salesperson_email_signature></p></bod","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217396,"name":"30 Day Out Tasks - to Notion","display_name":"30 Day Out Tasks - to Notion (v77os39p)","group_name":"ZAPIER","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body aria-label=\"To enrich screen reader interactions, please activate Accessibility in Grammarly extension settings\" data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1246.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1246.0\">\r\n<p>Event Name:&nbsp;<event_name><br />\r\n\tEvent Date:&nbsp;<event_date><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tEvent DJ:&nbsp;<djemployee1_name></p></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":30,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217397,"name":"Create Contact in Google Contacts","display_name":"Create Contact in Google Contacts (y62it4a3)","group_name":"ZAPIER","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1246.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1246.0\">\r\n<p><strong>FIRST NAME:</strong>&nbsp;<first_name><br />\r\n\t<strong>LAST NAME</strong>: <last_name><br />\r\n\t<strong>PHONE NUMBER</strong>:&nbsp;<cell_phone><br />\r\n\t<strong>EMAIL ADDRESS</strong>:&nbsp;<email><br />\r\n\t<strong>EVENT DATE</strong>:&nbsp;<event_date><br />\r\n\t<strong>EVENT NAME</strong>:&nbsp;<event_name></p></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":1,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"initial_contact_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217398,"name":"Let’s Get Ready to Make Your Celebration Unforgettable!","display_name":"Meet Your DJ","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1235.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1235.0\">\r\n<p>Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tI&rsquo;m <djemployee1_first_name>, and I&rsquo;ll be your DJ for <event_name>! I&rsquo;m excited to work with you and make your celebration unforgettable. To get everything just right, I&rsquo;d love to set up a virtual meet-and-greet on Google Meet. This will give us a chance to connect face-to-face and discuss all the details for your big day!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>Quick Details Check:</strong> To kick things off, could you confirm these details for me?</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Event Date: <event_date_long></li>\r\n\t<li>Venue: <event_location></li>\r\n\t<li>Start Time: <start_time></li></ul>\r\n<p><strong>What to Expect:</strong> During this call, you&rsquo;ll have the chance to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Make sure that you&#39;re onboarded onto our app</li>\r\n\t<li>Discuss the vibe you&rsquo;re envisioning for each part ","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":1,"schedule_direction":"after","schedule_anchor":"booked_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"primary_dj","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217399,"name":"Event Quote from Xpress Entertainment","display_name":"Invoice for Corporate Events","group_name":"QUOTE","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1209.0\">\r\n<p>Hey <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tThank you for considering&nbsp;Xpress Entertainment for your upcoming event! We&rsquo;re thrilled to partner with you to make this occasion unforgettable. Below are the details of your quote:<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong>Event Details:</strong></span><br />\r\n\t<strong>Contact Person</strong>: <name> -&nbsp;<cell_phone><br />\r\n\t<strong>Date</strong>: <event_date_long><br />\r\n\t<strong>Time</strong>: <start_time>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<end_time><br />\r\n\t<strong>Location:</strong><br />\r\n\t<event_location><br />\r\n\t<event_location_formatted_address><br />\r\n\t&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><br />\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong>Package Inclusions:</strong></span><br />\r\n\tYour selected package includes:<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong><package_name> -&nbsp;</strong><package_price><br />\r\n\t<package_description><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<addon_","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217400,"name":"Your Photo Booth Gallery Is Ready!","display_name":"Your Photo Booth Pictures Are Ready!","group_name":"POST EVENT","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body aria-label=\"To enrich screen reader interactions, please activate Accessibility in Grammarly extension settings\" data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1261.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1261.0\">\r\n<p>Hello <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tWe hope you&#39;re still basking in the glow of an unforgettable day! It was truly an honor to be part of such a special celebration.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tWe&rsquo;re excited to share your Photo Booth Gallery, full of the fun, silly, and sweet memories your guests captured. You can view and download the images using the link below:<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t&#128073; \r\n\t<a href=\"<custom_field9>\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>CLICK HERE</strong></a>&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tFeel free to share the gallery with friends and family, the more laughs, the better!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tThank you again for choosing Xpress Entertainment. Wishing you both a lifetime of love, happiness, and dance parties. &#127926;&#128131;","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217401,"name":"ACTION REQUIRED: has officially BOOKED","display_name":"DJ Booking Notification Sales Notification","group_name":"EMPLOYEES","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1221.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1221.0\">\r\n<p>Hey <employee_names_list_comma_separated>!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tYou&#39;re&nbsp; \r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#00FF00;\">BOOKED</span>! Congrats! The client has signed all the documents and the event is now considered \r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#00FF00;\">BOOKED!</span><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t&nbsp;Please login to XpressDJsClient.com and <strong>confirm the event ASAP</strong>!&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tDJs: Please not only confirm the event but also be sure to introduce yourself to the client by <strong>clicking &quot;Confirm Booking&quot; Button</strong><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>EVENT INFORMATION:</strong></span><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>Contact Name:&nbsp;</strong><first_name>&nbsp; <last_name><br />\r\n\t<strong>Contact Phone:</strong>&nbsp;<cell_phone>&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<strong>Event Date:</strong> <event_date>","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217402,"name":"Hello from Zola! - We Have DJs Available for Your Wedding on","display_name":"Zola Lead - Initial Email","group_name":"LEADS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1221.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1221.0\">\r\n<p>Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tThank you for connecting with Xpress Entertainment via Zola! We&rsquo;re delighted to hear about your big day on <event_date>. Our motto is all about curating mesmerizing wedding experiences through music and technology, and we&rsquo;d love to bring that magic to your celebration.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tOur DJs are known for crafting the hottest playlists to keep the dance floor packed all night. Better yet, they come from diverse cultural backgrounds, ensuring a tailor-made experience that reflects your unique tastes and traditions. Whether you&rsquo;re looking for classic tunes, modern hits, or cross-cultural musical blends, we&rsquo;re here to make it happen.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tIf you&rsquo;d like to see us in action, check out our Instagram at \r\n\t<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/xpressdjs\" target=\"_bla","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217405,"name":"30 Days to Party Time! Let’s Lock In Your Vibes! (Time to Schedule a meeting!)","display_name":"We're Alive 6 (30 Days) (May 2025)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1270.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1270.0\">Hey <first_name>!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCan you believe it? We&rsquo;re officially 30 days away from the big day &mdash; and I couldn&rsquo;t be more excited to celebrate with you both! &#10024;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs your DJ, I want to make sure everything is lined up perfectly &mdash; from your ceremony music to your grand entrance and every dance-floor moment in between. To make that happen, it&rsquo;s time for our final planning meeting!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&#127908; <strong>Book Your Final DJ Planning Call Here</strong>:&#128073; <djemployee1_custom_employee_field1><br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring this meeting, we&rsquo;ll go over:\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Your music selections &amp; must-plays</li>\r\n\t<li>Your event timeline</li>\r\n\t<li>Any logistical details or questions</li>\r\n\t<li>Fun ways to personalize the soundtrack of your love story &#128149;</li></u","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":30,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client","all_employees","master_admin"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217406,"name":"A Little Gift from Us for Your Upcoming Wedding!","display_name":"Photobooth Promo May 2025","group_name":"FLASH SALES / PROMOS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1234.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1234.0\">\r\n<p>Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tWe&rsquo;re getting excited for your big day coming up! &mdash; it&rsquo;s almost time to celebrate! &#127882;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tTo help you get ahead (and add a little something extra to the celebration), we&rsquo;re running a special promotion this week just for our couples with upcoming weddings:<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>If your next payment&nbsp;is made by this Friday, we&rsquo;d love to gift you a free photo booth for your big day! </strong>&#128248;&#10024;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tWant to add printed photo prints for your guests to take home? You&rsquo;ll also get prints at half price if you choose to include them.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tNo pressure at all &mdash; just a small thank-you and a fun way to add even more memories to your celebration.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tLet us know if you&#39;d like to take advanta","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217407,"name":"Welcome to the Xpress Entertainment Family!","display_name":"Contact Villa Client","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1270.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1270.0\">\r\n<p>Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tI hope you&rsquo;re doing great! My name is Laura, and I&rsquo;m the office manager here at Xpress Entertainment. We&rsquo;re so excited to be your DJs for your upcoming <event_type> at Villa Toscana <event_date_month_name> <event_date_year> &mdash;it&rsquo;s one of our favorite venues, and we can&rsquo;t wait to bring the vibes for your big day!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tIf you have any questions or need help at any point, I&rsquo;m here for you and happy to assist with anything.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tTo get started, I&rsquo;d love for you to download our planning app, Vibo 2.0, which is available on the \r\n\t<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vibo-2-0/id1523045467\" target=\"_blank\">App Store</a> and \r\n\t<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vibodj&amp;hl=en_US\">Google Play.</a> This app is w","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217408,"name":"3 Days After Booking - to Notion","display_name":