-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1239.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1239.0\">Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCongrats on booking your <event_type> at Villa Toscana &mdash; and welcome to the Xpress Entertainment family! We&rsquo;re so excited to be your entertainment team and can&rsquo;t wait to help make your big day unforgettable.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo kick things off, we&rsquo;d love to schedule a quick call so we can introduce ourselves, learn about your vision, and answer any questions you may have. You can pick a time that works best for you here:&nbsp; \r\n<a href=\"https://api.leadconnectorhq.com/widget/booking/cPllfYSeHEB1DRTsraIK\"><strong>CLICK HERE</strong></a><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<hr /><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>OUR APP, VIBO</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">To help you start planning the music and timeline, we use an amazing tool called Vibo.</span><","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":250,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client","master_admin"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217413,"name":"Book Call With DJ","display_name":"Book Call With DJ","group_name":"GENERAL","subject":"","body_html":"Hi <first_name>! Here’s the best link to schedule a quick call with <djemployee1_stage_name>: <djemployee1_custom_employee_field2>\r\n\r\nIt’s connected directly to <djemployee1_first_name>'s calendar, so you can pick a time that works best for you. Talk soon!","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"company","sched_send_to":[],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217414,"name":"Let’s Schedule a Call!","display_name":"Schedule a call invite link","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1270.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1270.0\">\r\n<p>Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tThanks for reaching out! The easiest way to set up a call is by using the link below&mdash;it&rsquo;s connected directly to <djemployee1_stage_name>&#39;s calendar, so you can choose a time that works best for you:<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t&#128073; <djemployee1_custom_employee_field2><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tLooking forward to chatting and going over the details of your big day!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tBest,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<company_email_signature></p></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217415,"name":"Review Request - From Drew","display_name":"Review Request - From Drew","group_name":"GENERAL","subject":"","body_html":"Hey <first_name>! It was such a blast being your DJ — I still think about how fun your wedding was! &#128516; When you have a sec, would you mind leaving a quick Google review? It helps me out a ton and means the world to small businesses like mine. Here’s the link: https://g.page/r/CS0a3uVwvUzJEAE/review\r\nThanks again, and wishing you both all the best!\r\n\r\n– DJ Drew &#127911;","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"company","sched_send_to":[],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217416,"name":"IMPORTANT: Let’s Get You Set Up with Your Wedding Planning App","display_name":"Have Not Joined Vibo Since Booking","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body aria-label=\"To enrich screen reader interactions, please activate Accessibility in Grammarly extension settings\" data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1270.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1270.0\">Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe&rsquo;re so excited to be your entertainment team for the big day! Whether you booked us directly or through one of our amazing venue partners, we can&rsquo;t wait to celebrate with you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo get started, we need you to join our wedding planning app &ndash; Vibo DJ. This app is where you&rsquo;ll share your music preferences, special moments, timeline details, and more. Filling it out early helps us either match you with the DJ that best fits your style or give your already-assigned DJ the tools they need to bring your vision to life.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you haven&rsquo;t downloaded the app yet, here&rsquo;s how:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&#128241; Download for iPhone ( \r\n<a h","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217417,"name":"Has not joing Vibo after Booking (Button)","display_name":"Has not joing Vibo after Booking (Button)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"Hi <first_name>! This is Laura from Xpress Entertainment. We’re excited to be part of your big day! To start planning your music, please download the Vibo DJ app and join your event here: <custom_field7>\r\n\r\niPhone: xpressdjs.com/viboapple\r\nAndroid: xpressdjs.com/vibogoogle\r\n\r\nLet me know if you need help! \r\n","is_activ