please activate Accessibility in Grammarly extension settings\" data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1256.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1256.0\">\r\n<p>Event Name:&nbsp;<event_name><br />\r\n\tClient First name:&nbsp;<first_name><br />\r\n\tClient Last name:&nbsp;<last_name><br />\r\n\tClient Email Address:&nbsp;<email><br />\r\n\tClient Phone Number:&nbsp;<cell_phone><br />\r\n\tDate of Event <event_date><br />\r\n\tEvent Vibo Link:&nbsp;<custom_field7><br />\r\n\tAssigned DJ: <djemployee1_employeeid><br />\r\n\tEvent Date:&nbsp;<event_date></p></body>\r\n</html>\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":215,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217430,"name":"Referral Opportunity – 's |","display_name":"Sending Lead to Another DJ","group_name":"VENDORS","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body aria-label=\"To enrich screen reader interactions, please activate Accessibility in Grammarly extension settings\" data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1252.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1252.0\">\r\n<p>Hi Friendor!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tI hope you&rsquo;re doing well! We were recently contacted by <first_name> regarding their upcoming <event_type> on <event_date> at &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<event_location>. Unfortunately, Xpress Entertainment is already booked for that date, but since we always want to take care of our clients, we shared your name as a trusted option.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tHere are a few quick details about the event:<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tEvent Type: <event_type><br />\r\n\tDate: <event_date><br />\r\n\tVenue: <event_location><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tClient Name: <name><br />\r\n\tClient Email: <email><br />\r\n\tClient Phone Number: <home_phone><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tAdditional Booking Notes they shared:&nbsp;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<comments><br />\r\n","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217431,"name":"Days Out! Let’s Start Planning the Music!","display_name":"We're Alive 5 (70 Days) (NEW 10-2025)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body aria-label=\"To enrich screen reader interactions, please activate Accessibility in Grammarly extension settings\" data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1267.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1267.0\">Hey <first_name>!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe&rsquo;re officially about 70 days away from your big day, and it&rsquo;s starting to get real! &#129346;Now&rsquo;s the perfect time to start filling out your Vibo DJ App, which is where you&rsquo;ll organize all the music details for your wedding.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHere&rsquo;s what to focus on right now:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&#9989; Answer the questions inside your Vibo event; these help our team learn about your vision, vibe, and preferences.<br />\r\n&#9989; Start shaping your playlists, don&rsquo;t stress about final song versions just yet! A general idea of your dance floor style and key moments (like your first dance or ceremony songs) is all we need for now.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<stro","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":70,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217432,"name":"We're Alive (70 Days)","display_name":"We're Alive (70 Days)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"Hey <first_name>! We’re 70 days out &#127881;\r\n\r\nNow’s the time to fill out your Vibo DJ App, answer the questions & start adding song ideas (no need for finals yet).\r\nHere’s your link &#128073; <custom_field7>\r\n\r\nAt 30 days out, you’ll get an email to book your planning call with your DJ! &#127911;","is_active":true,"is_sms":true,"djep_was_enabled":true,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":70,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["c0d3e855-ac0c-4a14-afdf-c00f7b5dbec5","5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217433,"name":"BOOKING CONFIRMATION FOR ON","display_name":"BOOKED WL (Vendor Notification)","group_name":"BOOKED","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body aria-label=\"To enrich screen reader interactions, please activate Accessibility in Grammarly extension settings\" data-gr-ext-installed=\"\" data-new-gr-c-s-check-loaded=\"14.1260.0\" data-new-gr-c-s-loaded=\"14.1260.0\">Hello,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis is confirmation that we have received a booking request for&nbsp;<event_date_long>.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you&#39;re receiving this email, we are available for the date requested and the event is now considered \r\n<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\"><strong> \r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> \r\n\t\t<span style=\"background-color:#008000;\">&quot;BOOKED&quot;</span></span></strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Please find the details that we have, and notify us immediately if any of this information is inaccurate.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tFor your convenience we have attached the invoice for this event, which can be paid via Zelle (office@xpressdjs.com)</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em><strong>\r\n<span sty","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":250,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":["5704490c-b089-4f5f-9756-0523c45b5daa"],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"legacy_djep_id":217434,"name":"Updated Agreement & Service Details","display_name":"Updated Agreement & Service Details","group_name":"BOOKING AGREEMENT","subject":"","body_html":"<html>\r\n<head>\r\n\t<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>Hi <first_name>,<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tI hope you&rsquo;re doing well! &#128075;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tPer our recent conversation, we have updated your booking to reflect the new services/package changes, thank you again for working through the details with us! &#127881;<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>&#128230; Updated Package / Services:</strong><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>PACKAGE</strong>:&nbsp;<package_name><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<package_description><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<b>ADDONS:</b><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<addon_list_no_prices><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<strong>&#128179; Updated Payment Schedule</strong><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tYour payment schedule has also been adjusted accordingly. You can review the updated totals, due dates, and agreement at the link below:<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t&#128073;&nbsp; \r\n\t<a href=\"esignaturelink:25849\">esignaturelink:25849</a><br />\r\n\t<br />\r\n\tPlease review and sign the revised agreement at your earliest convenience so we can lock everything in an","is_active":true,"is_sms":false,"djep_was_enabled":false,"schedule_enabled":false,"schedule_days":0,"schedule_direction":"before","schedule_anchor":"event_date","sched_status_ids":[],"sched_event_type_ids":[],"schedule_from":"master_admin","sched_send_to":["primary_client"],"review_reasons":[]},{"lega